{"tid":874622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傅振中帶隊「看珠西」：中華人民復興就係呢一刻喇！","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T12:42:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d529934b4ee747f3d424c2b26db3e2d3a9a0d05","tid":874622,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540369040_b0a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540369040_b0a8.jpg&h=ef1a2247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋今日通車，全國政協副主席梁振英昨日於Facebook發文，呼籲同學老師一同「走大橋，看珠西」。親中團體「保衛香港運動」今日就組團乘巴士由香港到珠海，召集人傅振中更不斷大叫口號「中國萬歲」，更揚言「中華人民復興就係呢一刻喇！係咪呀！」<br />\n<br />\n「保衛香港運動」一行約40人，今早於旺角乘搭直通巴到珠海口岸，下午抵步後到珠海酒樓午宴，同日回港。傅振中與「保衛香港運動」一眾成員抵達大橋珠海口岸後表現興奮，不斷揮動預先準備的國旗和區旗，又拿著印有「熱烈恭賀港珠澳大橋首日通車」合照，並高呼「祖國萬歲」。<br />\n<br />\n他更在口岸門口拍片留念，指：「見證國家世紀工程，人類偉大的歷史建築，我哋做中華人民兒女係咪感到好自豪呀？係！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181024/58830501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58830501&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=884d7e4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58830501&h=81bf66fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181024/58830501</a>"},{"pid":"3629cd014864875d5e74f452d496226cffc1b5e4","tid":874622,"uid":52605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"復咩興呀?<br />\n講都唔識講 扣你維穩費吖啦"},{"pid":"ea4b1d19f41227892ae92918fc34486dafe9224e","tid":874622,"uid":12021,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c15caeacac03b60357a8bbc57fbb8612c5ddd55","tid":874622,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"